channel.title: Help with client!
channel.description: Okay, i am tryin to play moparscape for the first time. so i just went to the client, typed in a username and password that im sure nobody else has, typed in the correct ip (soulsplit.com) and even entered the port by clicking file and then new port, but when i try to log in it says logging in please wait and then it says server is down or something. What do I do??? Please help!!! :confused: :confused: :confused:
